title.rendered: Celebrity Fashion Face-Off: Kim Kardashian vs. Khloe Kardashian

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Looks like the Kardashian sisters have more in common that just first names that start with the letter “K.”

As you can see here, the dress Kim Kardashian and Carrie Underwood both fancy was also recently worn by Khloe Kardashian.

Who do you think looks better in it, Kim or Khloe?
